<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ xīn jiāo jí, wǒ xīn jiāo jí, zhǔ a wǒ men guì xià qiú nǐ,
 jié jìng jiào huì, chéng wèi shèng jié, zhè yàng cái shì nǐ de xīn fù,
 mù rén zì lì, yáng wú rén lǐng, shān gǎng shēn gǔ dōu yǒu hǎn shēng,
 qī dài jiào huì fù xìng, zhēn lǐ hé yī, zhǔ a wǒ men guì xià qiú nǐ.
 kě wàng jiào huì fù xìng, zhēn lǐ hé yī, zhǔ a wǒ men guì xià qiú nǐ.\001
 shì dào bài huài hēi àn, zhēn lǐ guāng míng, zhǔ a kěn qiú shèng líng yǐn lǐng.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ xīn jiāo jí 迦南451</title>
